A '''Gold Chest''' with red locks can be found in the [[Shade Catacombs]] during the [[Shades of Mort'ton (minigame)|Shades of Mort'ton]] [[minigame]]. A [[gold key red]] is needed to open the chest, after which the key dissolves.

==Possible rewards==
{{DropLogProject|jagex=yes}}
{{Average drop value|mob=Gold Chest (red)|killname=opening}}

===Zealot robes===
''There is a 1/128 chance of hitting the zealot robes drop table. The player will obtain pieces in the following order, if they are not owned: boots, helm, robe bottom, and robe top. If the player owns all pieces, the rest of the drop table is rolled.''
{{DropsTableHead}}
